                        </p>
                        <p>
                          <form class = 'body' action= '/admin/our_story' method="POST">
                            <textarea name='our_story[new_name_body]' cols= "70" rows= "7">Why? Because when we first opened, virtually every outdoor expedition in the Steamboat Springs region — whether skiing, cycling, rafting, or climbing — made sure to pack into their essential provisions the one thing that made a successful day of adventure certain. Backcountry Provisions fare! Today, we’re pleased to unveil a new name and look to better embody our continued commitment to you and adventurers of every kind.</textarea>
